one of the Sahaja yogis said there was a Garuda.

00:39:22.002 --> 00:39:26.592
Couldn't see it. See Mother, see, there is a Garuda.

00:39:26.597 --> 00:39:30.008
Got out from the car and I looked up.

00:39:30.005 --> 00:39:38.554
Really, there was a cloud just like a Garuda going sideways. Just like a Garuda!

00:39:38.554 --> 00:39:44.024
You see, on the way I never saw this gentleman. (unclear

