You haven’t seen a photograph of Mine in Brahmapuri?

00:40:01.216 --> 00:40:05.784
You’ve seen that one? He must have
shown you, Yogi had it with him.

00:40:05.784 --> 00:40:11.324
Where with the rainbow, My face is there.

00:40:13.344 --> 00:40:15.844
Must get copy of all these, I think.

00:40:15.820 --> 00:40:18.320
I think we have got a copy of that here in Australia.

00:40:18.320 --> 00:40:21.886
You have? And the one in which, in a photograph…

