00:40:56.695 --> 00:40:59.195
How at that right moment they
take the photograph.

00:41:04.487 --> 00:41:09.700
Must be something, some sort of a communication, because nobody takes photograph of a rainbow.

00:41:12.520 --> 00:41:18.758
The first photograph that appeared in the sky, they told Me there was a funny thing happening in the sky.

00:41:18.751 --> 00:41:21.251
I said, “What happened?”

00:41:21.251 --> 00:41:28.057
First one cloud became very bright, (full of vibrations ?)

00:41:28.044 --> 00:41:35.587
and it started forming a shape of Ganesha, so we took the photograph.

00:41:35.599 --> 00:41:42.058
And then from there, lots of rays sort of going on the sides.

00:41:42.068 --> 00:41:48.494
And when the whole thing disappeared, then the peace came down.

00:41:51.324 --> 00:42:02.418
But so to attract that attention also, I’m sure this Paramchaitanya must be working some tricks,

00:42:02.438 --> 00:42:06.678
otherwise how at the right time you take the photograph.

00:42:08.552 --> 00:42:13.828
Yes because, so many photos are taken..

00:42:15.214 --> 00:42:17.714
Some get the thing.

00:42:21.250 --> 00:42:26.232
In one photograph Ganesha is just standing
behind Me. Absolutely. His blue body and eyes.

00:42:26.248 --> 00:42:31.012
But one can doubt it. One can think that
it’s a stuff one kept there or something.

00:42:31.003 --> 00:42:32.872
I mean, if you have to talk.

00:42:32.872 --> 00:42:36.902
But this one is too much to have a photograph.

00:42:39.703 --> 00:42:43.893
This Paramchaitanya is trying all
tricks to convince you about Me.

00:42:43.898 --> 00:42:46.625
We are already convinced, you see.

00:42:46.645 --> 00:42:50.905
But I don’t know about the world at large.

00:42:50.905 --> 00:42:55.075
They’ll sit down and find out, this is this, this is this.

00:42:55.921 --> 00:43:01.581
You know the famous photo series of the
rays of light, You know that very old one.

00:43:01.581 --> 00:43:06.411
There was somebody taking a photograph
at the same time, and it wasn’t on it.

00:43:06.397 --> 00:43:10.548
There are so many like that.

00:43:10.533 --> 00:43:14.557
In Calcutta you see, they were taking My photographs

00:43:14.557 --> 00:43:20.338
and Talwar’s daughter-in-law just prayed, “Mother, I want to have some miraculous photograph.”

00:43:20.338 --> 00:43:24.138
So the sun and moon both appeared behind Me.

00:43:36.958 --> 00:43:42.083
The photographs where there are angels and
you see all the deities sitting behind Me

00:43:42.102 --> 00:43:47.943
was taken by a boy who was in first year medicine.

00:43:47.951 --> 00:43:52.175
Brought it to Me. He said, “I don’t
know what’s wrong with my camera.

00:43:52.186 --> 00:43:56.835
I don’t know what has come out is this.”

00:43:56.835 --> 00:44:01.716
He said, “Mother, I am sorry. You see, I don’t
know. Just this funny thing has come out,

00:44:01.717 --> 00:44:04.217
You see, the thing I can’t understand.”

00:44:04.213 --> 00:44:05.767
Wanted to take My photograph,

00:44:05.767 --> 00:44:09.900
I have come up so little as that
and all the deities sitting there.

00:44:09.890 --> 00:44:13.900
He couldn’t understand that how it happened.

00:44:13.899 --> 00:44:18.759
And he had lots of them, one after
another, which you have seen all of you.
